 depends on the system parameters, in\nparticular distances between the nodes, and also on which part of the secrecy\nrate region the system is to operate at.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 17:52:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2019 18:28:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-13"}
