rra predator-prey model.\nFurthermore, environmental fluctuations with positive auto-correlations can\npromote persistence of evolving populations and persistence of diseases in\npatchy landscapes. While our results help close the gap between the persistence\ntheories for deterministic and stochastic systems, we highlight challenges for\nfuture research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 18:01:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Sep 2018 20:49:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2019 18:29:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-28"}
