17 is also discussed. Our study advocates that the tidal deformability\nnot only provides us information on the EOS, but may also give insights into\nthe multi-layer structure and elastic properties of compact star models\ncomposed of CCS quark matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2018 12:40:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-14"}
