a examples, we show that BINGO is superior in\ndealing with poor time resolution and it is computationally feasible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2018 14:50:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jul 2019 09:01:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2020 12:46:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-16"}
